Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-Mama...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Krv...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť je vždy jedna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je len jedna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nikto nezmení budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nedá sa zmeniť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kto?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kto je tam?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Asi som sa sem nedostal včas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.28,0:04:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nepribližujte sa k nám.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak sa k nám priblížite, zabijem vás.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som riaditeľ kampusu CLAMP.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.86,0:04:13.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prišiel som sem po tom, čo som dostal správu od Tokiko Magami.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.66,0:04:18.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aby som zapečatil Posvätný meč do Sľúbeného dňa
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,v strede nášho pentagramu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.44,0:04:30.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Musíme sa poponáhľať aj pre jej dobro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.07,0:04:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nemal som sa vracať do Tokia...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Každému okolo seba prinášam tragédiu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Všetci okolo mňa sú nešťastní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie je to tvoja vina.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prestaň sa obviňovať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chceš povedať, že je to osud?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keby som tu nebol...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keby som tu nebol...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.85,0:05:16.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kotori nemusela čeliť tomuto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tu som.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kto si?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som niekto, kto prechádza snami.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prechádzaš snami?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sme v tvojom sne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.66,0:06:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A ty sa nikdy nezobudíš z tohto sna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.17,0:06:38.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretože tvoje srdce sa odmietlo ešte niekedy zobudiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vedela si, čo sa stane v budúcnosti
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a preto si zvolila tento postup.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Z vlastnej vôle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Si kvalifikovaná na to byť jasnovidcom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Byť svedkom tej tragédie,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.25,0:06:56.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,teda zrodu druhého Posvätného meča...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite si to vedela.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Že budúcnosť sa blíži.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.96,0:07:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Viem to, pretože som jasnovidec ako ty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jasnovidec? Ten, kto prechádza snami?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.70,0:07:09.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som Kotori Monou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kto si?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kakyou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.85,0:07:20.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kakyou Kuzuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bol si tu celý čas?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budem tu navždy spať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mohla by som vidieť tvoju tvár?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Samozrejme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale nie tu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Môžeme ísť do môjho sna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je nádherné miesto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pán Kakyou Kuzuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Volaj ma Kakyou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Si ako ja...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Niekto, kto je zapletený do konca sveta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.32,0:08:06.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vieme, čo sa stane v budúcnosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť tvojho milovaného brata a Kamuiho.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.93,0:08:15.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Preto si sa kvôli nim obetovala.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kvôli tej jedinej nádeji.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vieš všetko, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kvôli komu to robíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie je nikto na svete, kvôli komu by som to urobil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neexistuje už v žiadnom svete.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nikde.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bol si do tej osoby zaľúbený.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:45.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tvoje smutné pocity prúdia do mňa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To by si nemala.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nesynchronizuj sa s mojím srdcom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zomrieš od bolesti, ktorú bude cítiť tvoje srdce.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prestaň plakať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dosť o mne.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.42,0:09:09.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že sa ti tvoje želanie splní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, Kakyou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je vážne pekné miesto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Za malý okamih sa Kamuiho hviezda zobudí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A vtedy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.87,0:09:28.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto dievča...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blíži sa to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čas voľby.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.35,0:09:40.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tak rýchlo sa blíži...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:54.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mozgové vlny, krvný tlak a tep sú stabilné.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale mali by sme ju nechať oddychovať a uvidíme, ako jej bude.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.70,0:10:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Avšak pre psychologické poradenstvo budeme potrebovať veľa času.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.84,0:10:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Preberieme zodpovednosť a budeme tvoju sestru liečiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prosím, nemaj obavy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mám niečo od Tokiko, čo ti chcem ukázať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcem ostať tu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui, dám na ňu pozor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Choď.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Odteraz budeme všetci traja spolu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.11,0:10:44.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tento kampus bol vytvorený kvôli Sľúbenému dňu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.29,0:10:49.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aby chránil Posvätný meč až do Sľúbeného dňa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.16,0:10:53.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Posvätný meč je jediný, ktorý môže Kamui držať.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo sú potom dva Posvätné meče?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.97,0:11:02.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Posvätný meč, ktorý niekto zobral zo svätyne Togakushi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A tento druhý Posvätný meč, ktorý porodila Tokiko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak je to jediný meč, prečo sú dva?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ani k tomu nepoznám odpoveď.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.34,0:11:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokiko Magami mi len povedala, aby som chránil Posvätný meč.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je niečo, čím som sa podľa nej mal riadiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.36,0:11:27.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Povedala, že v okamihu jej smrti sa táto bábika rozbije.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ako ste vedeli, kde je Posvätný meč?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj to mi ukázala tá bábika.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tým smerom je svätyňa Togakushi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už mi aspoň trochu veríš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ukážem ti ešte niečo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto ti zanechala Tokiko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.55,0:11:52.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keď budeš toto vidieť, už som porodila Posvätný meč
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a už nebudem žiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.82,0:11:58.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Preto ti takto poviem niečo veľmi dôležité.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui, už nie je čas.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Teraz si musíš vybrať svoj osud.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Byť Drakom nebies, jedným zo Siedmych pečatí,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.03,0:12:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,alebo byť Drakom zeme, jedným zo Siedmych anjelov.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.30,0:12:15.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Osud sveta sa týmto rozhodnutím drasticky zmení.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.78,0:12:19.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Byť Drakom nebies a želať si prítomnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Alebo byť Drakom zeme a želať si revolúciu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prítomnosť alebo revolúcia...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak si budeš želať prítomnosť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,budúcnosť ľuďmi zamorenej Zeme,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,bude musieť byť ponechaná ľuďom samotným.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Potom si musíš želať
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,odpor voči zničeniu sveta.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak si želáš revolúciu,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,svet bude stratený a civilizácia zničená,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.81,0:12:50.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ale planéta zvaná Zem by určite smerovala k znovuzrodeniu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prítomnosť alebo revolúcia.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui, ty rozhodneš o budúcnosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O vlastnej budúcnosti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.82,0:13:07.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zastavte niekto Kamuiho...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Takto to dievča...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.83,0:13:11.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Niekto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zastavte niekto Kamuiho!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo to, preboha, bolo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Niečo sa muselo stať Kamuimu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,V pentagrame.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pentagram?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tá škola!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Želať si prítomnosť alebo revolúciu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čas vybrať si konečne nastal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale je len jedna budúcnosť, sestrička.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vidíš v snoch budúcnosť,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.86,0:13:48.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ale tej budúcnosti sa nemôžeš nikdy dotknúť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ani ty nemôžeš zmeniť budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Osud?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo je osud?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.41,0:14:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť, o ktorej už bolo rozhodnuté.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je naozaj divné!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.69,0:14:09.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nie je proste možné, aby o budúcnosti už bolo rozhodnuté.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Možno ty budeš schopný zmeniť budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretože si "Kamui".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Staň sa silným, Kamui.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aby si mohol ochrániť Kotori a Fumu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aby si mohol ochrániť tých, ktorých máš rád.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.21,0:14:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Byť Drakom nebies a želať si prítomnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Alebo byť Drakom zeme a želať si revolúciu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ty si vyberieš budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tvoju vlastnú budúcnosť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:48.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neviem, čo by sa malo stať s týmto svetom.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.66,0:14:53.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Je mi jedno, či budem Drakom nebies alebo zeme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja len...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vtedy som ti sľúbil,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.10,0:15:02.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,že ak sa ti niečo stane, ochránim ťa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A to sa nezmení.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nikdy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.28,0:15:11.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vraj trvá desať až dvadsať rokov, než vznikne takáto farba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale myslím, že to chcem skúsiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je môj sen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Desať... Možno dvadsať rokov...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.26,0:15:21.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.20,0:15:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Len chcem, aby Kotori a Fuma boli šťastní.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chcem ochrániť miesto, kde môžu šťastne žiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je všetko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že si si vybral.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prítomnosť pred revolúciou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť Draka nebies, jedného zo Siedmych pečatí.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vybral si si.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo je to s tebou?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak si sa stal Drakom nebies,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,mojím osudom je stať sa Drakom zeme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O čom to hovoríš, Fuma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dva Posvätné meče...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dve budúcnosti...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Som tvoja druhá hviezda.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.98,0:16:20.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ja som druhý "Kamui"!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.05,0:16:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Č-Čo je to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kotori...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prosím, buď v poriadku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kotori!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kotori!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Máš dobrý hlas, Kamui.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.76,0:17:38.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vieš, čo práve robíš?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Samozrejme.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zem túži po revolúcii.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.01,0:17:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Revolúcia, ktorej sa ľudia nepostavia do cesty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.58,0:17:55.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stanem sa Drakom zeme, zabijem Drakov nebies
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a vyhubím všetkých, čo znečisťujú Zem.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.48,0:18:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-Niečo nie je s tebou v poriadku, Fuma...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto je tvoj osud.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Braček.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fuma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.35,0:18:33.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kotori...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Si ďalší.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Niekto je v tom dievčati.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kto je to?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.68,0:18:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto dievča si neželá Kamuiho smrť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jasnovidec...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.02,0:19:05.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hýbeš jej mŕtvym telom tak, že si vstúpil do jej smrteľného sna, však?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jasnovidec, ktorý ovláda mŕtvych.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prečo sa mi staviaš do cesty?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drak zeme?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Odpovedz mi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Určite ťa zabijem!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kamui!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nemožné...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kamui...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toto si chcela?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.14,0:20:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pretože si mala potenciál stať sa jasnovidcom,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,bol som schopný vstúpiť do tvojho sna.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.84,0:20:39.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Máme sny dokonca aj v okamihu smrti.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Vedel som, že sa to stane.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aj keď poznám budúcnosť, nemôžem nič urobiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Osoba, ktorá bola pre teba taká vzácna... A ty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.13,0:20:54.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nikoho z vás som nedokázal zachrániť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.96,0:20:55.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Zachránil si Shiroua.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To je všetko, čo som potrebovala.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A tiež som zo sna vedela,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,že môj brat a Kamui
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,sa budú snažiť navzájom zabiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale tiež som nemohla nič urobiť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.41,0:21:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Na Kamuiho čaká smútok silnejší než smrť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bolesť zo straty teba.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.85,0:21:17.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A potom zraňovanie osoby,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,ku ktorej vzhliadal ako k staršiemu bratovi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Verím mu.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.46,0:21:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Verím, že Shirou neprehrá, nech bude akokoľvek zranený.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.43,0:21:32.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okrem toho je Shirou jediný, kto môže zachrániť môjho brata.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.87,0:21:36.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, Kakyou.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Už musím ísť.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.09,0:21:55.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kakyou...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.62,0:21:58.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ak uvidíš môjho brata a Kamuiho, prosím, povedz im,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,že ich oboch ľúbim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.03,0:22:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Že o budúcnosti ešte nie je rozhodnuté.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.44,0:22:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O budúcnosti ešte nie je rozhodnuté.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.29,0:22:31.29,Style1,,0,0,0,,Preklad a časovanie: Dashio
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.29,0:22:34.29,Style1,,0,0,0,,Korekcia: Ayamee
